6.00	Namdroling_Monastery	Namdroling Monastery	Located in Bylakuppe — part of the Mysore district of the state of Karnataka — the monastery is home to a sangha community of over five thousand lamas (both monks and nuns), a religious college (or shedra) and hospital.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/55/Namdroling.jpg/250px-Namdroling.jpg
